		<td><b>Smash Bros Demake</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Here's a title screen for a Smash Bros Demake.<br /><br />Mario, Peach, and Link are in the background, and Samus, Mega Man, and Kirby are sprites. In Metroid, Samus doesn't have a black outline, because the background of the levels is black. I modified the sprite to have a black outline, so the green highlights on Samus as well as Mega Man's face are another layer of sprites (they share a palette -- green, tan, and white).

		
