	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Are we posting Smash Bros NES stuff? I made something a while ago as well!<br /><br /><img src="http://orig01.deviantart.net/ef4f/f/2016/032/d/2/super_smash_bros_duel_by_dragondeplatino-d9q4bcs.png" alt="Image" /><br /><br />I was wasn't really paying attention to size restrictions when making this but I think the palettes, character choices and general idea could work. Many of these work without overlays and could be edited down to 3x4 sprites. Theoretically, a NES Smash Bros game would be limited to 1v1 matches to prevent flickering. My character choices were all 1st party characters that originated on or before the NES, but I suppose characters like Yoshi could work as well.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
